# Copy to .env.local and fill in to let the notebook read the LIVE study database
# directly (it otherwise reproduces everything from the bundled de-identified,
# numeric-only snapshot with zero configuration). .env.local is git-ignored.
#
# Option A — direct PostgreSQL (most "reads the database directly"):
#   the Railway public connection string from the study's environment
# DATABASE_PUBLIC_URL=postgresql://USER:PASSWORD@HOST:PORT/DBNAME
#
# Option B — the deployed app's de-identified admin export over HTTPS:
# STUDY_BASE_URL=https://your-study-deployment.example.app
# ADMIN_TOKEN=your-admin-token
